reviews: Love them. I’ve ordered them twice! Love the fit. They are lightweight, and comfy!
Best investment. It’s easy to use, easy to clean. A big helper for delicious coffee
Love these. It’s a little difficult to get the salt and pepper in them, but they easily grind and I love the look!
I had a hammock and lost the straps that came with it. These are just as great. I was worried about the quality, but easily held my friend, who is approx 400lbs.
Don’t hesitate. I love this! It’s super simple! Feels like I’m just walking out of a salon!

I would definitely order this again. I bought this for a tapestry that I bought at an auction, it’s thin so the magnets held it perfectly! It’s very simple and elegant, so doesn’t take away from the actual piece!
These are so sweet. I used them to make myself a garland, it was a simple project and these beads are super consistent, and really well made. I would order them again for sure!

I waited a few weeks before writing a review because I wanted to live with the bag for a bit. I use it everyday, and it easily carries all my stuff. I travel with a large agenda, an iPad, my phone and several personal items, hand cream, water bottle etc and it all comfortably fits. The bag looks better day after day, the later really is quite nice, and the reinforced straps are sturdy. Would recommend to friends, and know that I won’t have to buy it again! Great quality bag, don’t hesitate!
Really well made, looks great, and fit as expected for my son.
We ended up using this attached to a piece of Bristol board instead of hanging it. The gold dots come in two long strings, so do not display like the picture shows. I was disappointed.

review_title: You have to fluff them yourself!
reviews: I did not anticipate how long these would take to “fluff”. Actually I didn’t realize that they had to be fluffed at all until we were setting up. The colours are beautiful and they were a hit, at the party, but I didn’t have time to fluff them all!
This model is fantastic. Easy to use, super convenient to have when I'm on the road, or away from my normal espresso machine. It makes a good espresso shot! :D

Cooking is easy with the instant pot. It does require reading directions and recipies so you don't burn stuff to the bottom, so If you don't like to follow rules, an instant pot is not for you. It is super convenient and I use it at least once a week!! Some recipes are easier than others, some are quite complex. I'm really happy to have this in my kitchen.

No, seriously, you don't understand. About 3 years ago I bought these pants and winners and didn't realize until i got them home and started living in them just how comfy they are. Oh lord. They are a second skin. They flare at the bottom, they fit perfectly in the legs and ass and the length is perfect for me. The first pair I have has been used and abused. they are my go to for bing watching netflix, sick days at home, & rotten winter weekends when I stay inside, after three years of abuse, they look pretty ratty, so I'm happy to finally retire them, knowing I've found their perfect replacement. Dont hesitate to buy these... they are the holy grail of comfy pants. I love them.

I hesitated because if hats are not tall enough they slip off my head. I was worried this wouldn't fit as well as the ones I've tried on but balked at the inflated prices. This is super cozy and comfy and cute. I doubt I'll take it off my head this winter as we Canadians start the hibernation process.
